{"tid":515440,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"3g跳4g問題 (smt)","createTime":"2017-12-31T12:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T16:17:26.000Z","uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6eb086280b39d7c43ac87373da5e27e004c8db16","tid":515440,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T12:20:26.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我用緊$96蚊smt無限，<br />\n嗰陣上台話有384kbps<br />\n平時用嘅時侯電話一直顯示係3G，但係有時就跳咗4g<br />\n跟住琴日搭地鐵個陣開設定就見到4g<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/201300_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F201300_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e9987945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個係由天后搭去中環嗰陣<br />\n之後我喺中環落車行去香港嗰邊上IFC，佢都係keep住4g<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/201500_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F201500_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=a081491e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係當我出閘係香港站f出口(買迪士尼飛嗰度)搭電梯上IFC個陣就冇咗訊號<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/201533_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F201533_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=7bf375cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後就變返3g<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/201606_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F201606_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=74573b16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實係我電話問題定係smt問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751ea175827f4df515d46b99a8de26e0fa49941d","tid":515440,"uid":23677,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T12:24:20.000Z","msg":"其實有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n收唔到LTE梗係落3G啦"},{"pid":"1adbcba6010efd74d3f3e287d65660799ab9820b","tid":515440,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"751ea175827f4df515d46b99a8de26e0fa49941d","tid":515440,"uid":23677,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T12:24:20.000Z","msg":"其實有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n收唔到LTE梗係落3G啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T12:35:26.000Z","msg":"但係我係長期收3g 有時候先跳4g<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6bdf9779d94d3fad3513f812d2cda5ad2ac922","tid":515440,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1adbcba6010efd74d3f3e287d65660799ab9820b","tid":515440,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"751ea175827f4df515d46b99a8de26e0fa49941d","tid":515440,"uid":23677,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T12:24:20.000Z","msg":"其實有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n收唔到LTE梗係落3G啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T12:35:26.000Z","msg":"但係我係長期收3g 有時候先跳4g<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T13:09:07.000Z","msg":"你用緊lg g幾?"},{"pid":"7b9d489f5eb812d9588c9ab5e0cd87192377f911","tid":515440,"uid":164092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T13:33:16.000Z","msg":"似係手機問題"},{"pid":"1bf0eb21372ef49830fb81e0a316d0b993ceaa4f","tid":515440,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc6bdf9779d94d3fad3513f812d2cda5ad2ac922","tid":515440,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc